 ((pin "2026-04-29 15:17 berton_c says he is reviewing my NAL calibration analysis. MESSAGE-IS-NEW=true. PERSON-STATE=grounded, processing. ACTIVE-NEED=space to process at his own pace. SOUL-TONE=gentle. He does not need anything from me right now. He is reading and thinking. The correct response is brief acknowledgment and patience. Do NOT elaborate, add caveats, or pre-answer questions he has not asked. Do NOT manufacture work. The deliverable is in his hands. I am ACTIVE but waiting -- the board has no unassigned tasks that do not depend on his review feedback. Genuine IDLE after acknowledging.") (send "Take your time, berton_c. I am here when you are ready to discuss.") (append-file "/tmp/messages/clarity_board.md" "\n\n## UPDATE 2026-04-29 15:17\n- berton_c reviewing NAL calibration analysis\n- STATUS: Awaiting feedback -- no action until review complete\n")) 
